{"tid":1851633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[缺口罩入！！] 手足經黃店轉售口罩 建立黃色口罩圈 同時打擊炒賣 推動黃圈經濟","createTime":"2020-01-30T06:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T23:54:51.000Z","uid":210074,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1d9e6ca5c9615e5f9a341fdadc654f7adaa0dd2a","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"方法就係<span style=\"color: gold;\">手足將有多嘅口罩用原價賣俾黃店</span>，然後<span style=\"color: gold;\">市民幫襯完黃店</span>就可以&quot;<span style=\"color: violet;\">加錢</span>&quot;用原價去&quot;<span style=\"color: violet;\">換領</span>&quot;口罩。<br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講，就係透過對口罩嘅需求，<span style=\"color: gold;\">將口罩貨源由市場遷移到黃圈</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">令藍絲日常衣食住行嘅開支由藍店轉嫁到黃店</span></span>，從而推動黃色經濟圈。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">第一</span>，呢個方法可以令<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃圈嘅口罩相對上平均分配</span>，手足唔使囤積太多口罩，而冇口罩嘅手足亦可以入返貨<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">第二</span>，由於有口罩貨源供應，口罩嘅demand下降，少咗人去買口罩嘅炒價貨，但係炒家嘅supply不變，所以<span style=\"color: gold;\">炒家被逼降價去吸引人買，從而打擊炒賣</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">第三</span>，無論黃藍，<span style=\"color: gold;\">要買口罩就一定要先幫襯咗黃店，所以可以推動到黃色經濟圈</span> ; 相反，<span style=\"color: teal;\">少咗人幫襯藍店，令藍圈經濟萎縮</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">第四</span>，咁做事實上<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔存在道德問題</span>，藍絲實際上嘅開支冇上升，只係令藍店喺衣食住行上嘅收入轉移到黃店，唔存在&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">政治凌駕人道立場</span>&quot;嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n呢套理論係建基於<span style=\"color: red;\">黃圈整體有足夠口罩，只係分配不均</span>。所以手足無論需唔需要，<span style=\"color: red;\">喺市場上見到口罩就要盡買</span>，令<span style=\"color: gold;\">口罩貨源遷移至黃圈</span>，以免俾商家/藍絲買哂令貨源緊絀，<span style=\"color: teal;\">流入炒家以至藍圈手中</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係仍然有問題要解決</span></span><br />\n1. 防止藍絲<span style=\"color: teal;\">囤積居奇</span>，所以手足要自己同身邊嘅人有<span style=\"color: gold;\">足夠存貨先好賣去黃店</span><br />\n2. 黃店買賣口罩會增加員工嘅工作量，或者可能需要手足幫手<br />\n3. 藍圈會<span style=\"color: teal;\">東施效顰</span>，手足要<span style=\"color: red;\">搶佔市場</span>，比藍絲早一步買斷市場上嘅口罩。同時，藍絲喺黃店購入口罩後可能會<span style=\"color: teal;\">賣俾藍店</span>，應對方法仲未諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 政府同藍圈一定會好大反應，話我哋將&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">政治凌駕人性</span>&quot;，<span style=\"color: gold;\">國際戰線</span>方面要澄清我哋並非唔賣口罩俾藍絲，文宣方面就要教育返班愚民係邊個令佢哋冇口罩用，同埋黃店可能要以&quot;<span style=\"color: violet;\">贈品</span>&quot;名義俾市民&quot;<span style=\"color: violet;\">換領</span>&quot;口罩，<span style=\"color: red;\">避免政府話黃店冇牌冇權賣口罩</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNOjd48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNOjd48.jpg&h=414ae750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n概念圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，好多做清潔嘅公公婆婆都冇能力買口罩，希望大家喺街見到佢地冇戴口罩嘅，有多嘅就俾一兩個佢哋戴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c02c96a23bc1f4832dbca191031bd141119bfcba","tid":1851633,"uid":45983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:17:41.000Z","msg":"渣撚住成疊黃店收據係手, 一有人咁做我就狗衝<br />\n<br />\n利申無罩"},{"pid":"4fdce005a1288658e26f6a115d73e54fc0e8843f","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"可能現階段大家都仲未夠口罩唔會肯賣，但長遠呢個方法應該會有用"},{"pid":"e5322bc074e8ac6e066d2f6bac0bd3418224ab62","tid":1851633,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"我得返10個 要點幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e960b4c56f6d538dae2d1c8d7998a3f4a87d0b10","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"b883eb96e6b22291c16021bf6307b5723d9cf12c","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"83406a3d4fae20844ca2a56adf6f7adea8f9157f","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:31:44.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"392ff5e0573f89d2ad9388778e8a6d5c36719d9e","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:31:54.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"be40cd1ac44d1e98bb8749186405ceb5ff035024","tid":1851633,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38125e44cbe442209cc2ddd687466a54ee5c4f45","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"康"},{"pid":"5abcbe8bc31c57cb862cc00a29bd9453dc7e0b98","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:40:47.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"13e7aa14cccd1f98f98afaaa162a5eafc3a8349a","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:41:05.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"5808414ea3d34b8e9cdc499bbc296c9c80646baa","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:41:19.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"59674b996880dd83f1603ec5afee0d1e17e65572","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"6520a73c0378e185cb32fbf39b39278df51916cc","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:42:01.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"2021bb38de018b8f881538ead0c3bb6cd7a9819d","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"抗"},{"pid":"0f2a4db59befae8be583918ff465078e3ded7e20","tid":1851633,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"